-- Aya Dental Clinic (Clínica Aya Estudio Dental) - Digital dental clinic with English-speaking staff
('Aya Dental Clinic', 'Dental', 'Modern dental clinic in Madrid founded by Dr. May Rodríguez Villamizar, specializing in minimally invasive treatments with cutting-edge digital technology. All staff speak English, making it ideal for international patients and expats. Doctors have advanced training at top dentistry universities in America and Europe. Services include dental implants, orthodontics, tooth whitening, conservative dentistry, pediatric dentistry (odontopediatrics), endodontics, oral and maxillofacial surgery, periodontics (gum disease treatment including gingivitis and periodontitis), bone regeneration, veneers, dental crowns, inlays, implant prosthesis, and dental aesthetics. Fully digital clinic with intraoral scanners, 3D radiographs, and 3D printers for precision treatments. Located in the Tetuán neighborhood near Cuzco and Chamartín.', 'Av. de Brasil 17, 28020 Madrid', 'Madrid', 'Madrid', '+34 915 711 691', 'info@clinicaaya.es', 'https://www.clinicaaya.es/en/', true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW());
